  <div class="callout sand">
    <div class="callout-lbl">When the 529 Payments End — A Portfolio Gift</div>
    <p>The 529 contributions ($300/month combined) end by age 47. That $300/month, redirected to the taxable brokerage, compounds for 13 more years at 7% to add approximately <strong>$75,000</strong> to your retirement portfolio. Small amounts, long runway, big impact.</p>
