      <div class="rb-desc">No phased transitions. No "you work while I explore." You build it together, you end it together. The portfolio does the rest — no worrying about whether you have enough, because at $3.5M with a $95–100K spending need, you have a 30+ year plan with meaningful margin.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="rb-stats">
      <div class="rb-stat">
